## Dependencies

- CMake 3.16+
- Ninja
- SDL2
- OpenGL + GLU
- OpenAL

Ubuntu/Debian:
    sudo apt install cmake ninja-build libsdl2-dev libglu1-mesa-dev libopenal-dev

macOS:
    brew install cmake ninja sdl2 openal-soft

## Build

    mkdir build && cd build
    cmake -G Ninja ..
    ninja

## Run

From the project root (so it can find res/):

    ./build/cosmos
